Commentary Text: Harshal Patel to Hrithik Shokeen, out Caught by du Plessis!! Superb catch by Faf at mid-off. Commentary Text: M Bracewell to Suryakumar Yadav, out Caught by Shahbaz Ahmed!! A soft dismissal! Suryakumar Yadav had got off to a start tonight but he finds a way to get himself out.
